metadata.name: Shekardokht
metadata.description:
Wide-eyed, she is always searching for new experience
She plays these melodies on her piano, without knowing the notes.

_ 

I created this collection spontaniously. Later on, I added the small animations and the music to fit the static yet peaceful environment of Shekardokht's world.

10sec | 2736 x 2050 px | Music & Animation : Mojtaba Heidarpanah
